msgctxt "sn55.33:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.33:0.2"
msgid "4. Puññābhisandavagga "
msgstr "4. Overflowing Merit "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 33. Tatiyapuññābhisandasutta → tatiyābhisandasuttaṃ (bj) | abhisanda 3 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn55.33:0.3"
msgid "33. Tatiyapuññābhisandasutta "
msgstr "33. Overflowing Merit (3rd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn55.33:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, puññābhisandā kusalābhisandā sukhassāhārā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four kinds of overflowing merit, overflowing goodness that nurture happiness. "

msgctxt "sn55.33:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn55.33:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha … "

msgctxt "sn55.33:1.4"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn55.33:1.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ paṭhamo puññābhisando kusalābhisando sukhassāhāro. "
msgstr " "

#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn55.33:2.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako dhamme … pe … "
msgstr "the teaching … "

msgctxt "sn55.33:2.2"
msgid "saṅghe … pe …. "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn55.33:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako paññavā hoti udayatthagāminiyā paññāya samannāgato ariyāya nibbedhikāya sammā dukkhakkhayagāminiyā. "
msgstr "Furthermore, a noble disciple is wise. They have the wisdom of arising and passing away which is noble, penetrative, and leads to the complete ending of suffering. "

msgctxt "sn55.33:3.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ catuttho puññābhisando kusalābhisando sukhassāhāro. "
msgstr "This is the fourth kind of overflowing merit, overflowing goodness that nurtures happiness. "

msgctxt "sn55.33:3.3"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro puññābhisandā kusalābhisandā sukhassāhārā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four kinds of overflowing merit, overflowing goodness that nurture happiness.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.33:3.4"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

